name: MITHICAL
description: "Mithical.io is an NFT project utilizing Defi mechanics to offer self-repaying NFTs through a lossless mint process to its community. Across cultures myths describe magical kingdoms & beings that fascinate the human mind. As a community-driven NFT project we will resurrect these worlds on the Arbitrum blockchain. Our project will build on existing myths by molding authentic characters & narratives. The art is based on Japanese traditional art and myth."
